{"id": "1353643387810615398", "channel_id": "1353643387810615398", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "感謝各位守密人的支持！\n《忘卻前夜》OST：薩爾瓦多EP·蒼白的聖徒，今日發佈～歡迎大家收聽、下載及分享～如果有基於OST的二次創作，也歡迎分享給我們！ （二創請遵照同人規則，OST內容請勿商用）\n\n忘卻前夜OST：薩爾瓦多EP·蒼白的聖徒\n偉大的父啊，願您的光照耀世界。\n\n作曲：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\n規劃：B.I.A.V. Studio\n\n——◆——◆—— ◆◆◆ ——◆——◆——\n\nThank you for your support!\n\n《Morimens》OST：《Salvador EP·The Pale Saint》 was released today. \nWelcome everyone to listen, download and share. If you have secondary creations based on the OST, please also share them with us!\n (Please follow the rules of the fandom for secondary creations, and do not use the OST content for commercial purposes)\n\n《Morimens》OST：《Salvador EP·The Pale Saint》 \nGreat Father, may Your light shine upon the world.\n\nComposer：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\n\nPlanning：B.I.A.V. Studio", "timestamp": "2025-03-24T08:15:33.132000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 12}], "attachments": [{"id": "1353643388154544199", "filename": "EP__.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 303539, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1353643387810615398/1353643388154544199/EP__.jpg?ex=69ccd425&is=69cb82a5&hm=cd88c7a47d72fd71b69f75214caf83a3055eaca951f96c30a95cc42c5d64ae70&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1353643387810615398", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：薩爾瓦多EP·蒼白的聖徒", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1353643926606843974", "channel_id": "1353643387810615398", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**01.提燈長明-Eternal Lantern-**\n提燈將驅逐一切罪惡。\n你需虔誠悔過，流盡鮮血，方能將罪惡流出，升入天堂。\nThe lantern will drive away all sins.\nYou need to repent sincerely and shed all your blood before you can shed your sins and ascend to heaven.", "timestamp": "2025-03-24T08:17:41.591000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1353643926161981460", "filename": "1.-Eternal_Lantern-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 21092246, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1353643387810615398/1353643926161981460/1.-Eternal_Lantern-.wav?ex=69ccd4a5&is=69cb8325&hm=7a47a3d366c3a9bff6259ab96b358dde44cc846af73b98dda5e5772cce8880d5&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1353643387810615398", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：薩爾瓦多EP·蒼白的聖徒", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1353644055233298443", "channel_id": "1353643387810615398", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**02.盲目的聖徒-Blind Saint-**\n萬能的主啊，請祢賜我應受之罰。\nAlmighty Lord, please give me the punishment I deserve.", "timestamp": "2025-03-24T08:18:12.258000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1353644054851620945", "filename": "2.-Blind_Saint-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 40245656, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1353643387810615398/1353644054851620945/2.-Blind_Saint-.wav?ex=69ccd4c4&is=69cb8344&hm=f73e27d13c3d88c736b2f98af2ab90fc88296a4380eb517dffad0be18131242b&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1353643387810615398", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：薩爾瓦多EP·蒼白的聖徒", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1353644105762078843", "channel_id": "1353643387810615398", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**03.妄想-Delusion-**\n人們爭先恐後地廝殺，妄想這樣就能洗清自己的罪，率先踏入純淨無瑕的神國。\nPeople rushed to fight, hoping that they could wash away their sins and be the first to step into the pure and flawless kingdom of God.", "timestamp": "2025-03-24T08:18:24.305000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1353644105443315732", "filename": "3.-Delusion-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 25654520, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1353643387810615398/1353644105443315732/3.-Delusion-.wav?ex=69ccd4d0&is=69cb8350&hm=d462a62a2ee32d6a50e5906f81304ab80371eb82846f26315c965ae7b6485035&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1353643387810615398", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：薩爾瓦多EP·蒼白的聖徒", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1353644179158470691", "channel_id": "1353643387810615398", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**04.遠方的呼喚-Lord's Call-**\n靈魂深處的連結發出呼喚。\n騎士應約而至，來到主君的身邊。\nThe link deep in the soul called.\nThe knight came as promised and came to the side of the lord.", "timestamp": "2025-03-24T08:18:41.804000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1353644178793300020", "filename": "4.-Lords_Call-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 16992098, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1353643387810615398/1353644178793300020/4.-Lords_Call-.wav?ex=69ccd4e1&is=69cb8361&hm=c2c6e6bf5300f15bd3bf4f4d6c666142054a3ad5345300ed17d63b300dec1d2b&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1353643387810615398", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：薩爾瓦多EP·蒼白的聖徒", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1353644282971557929", "channel_id": "1353643387810615398", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**05.無私的善-Selfless Benevolence-**\n孩子，你願意幫我一個忙麼。\nChild, are you willing to do me a favor?", "timestamp": "2025-03-24T08:19:06.555000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1353644282606780426", "filename": "5.-Selfless_Benevolence-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 20925464, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1353643387810615398/1353644282606780426/5.-Selfless_Benevolence-.wav?ex=69ccd4fa&is=69cb837a&hm=04661bb9e8ef9fd2865f59596293306bde68793e96311f845b477d1b5bfbde12&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1353643387810615398", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：薩爾瓦多EP·蒼白的聖徒", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1353644388961620062", "channel_id": "1353643387810615398", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**06.血月-Blood Moon-**\n看啊，猩紅之月已經升起，所有罪人都將遭到淨化。\nLook, the scarlet moon has risen, and all sinners will be purified.", "timestamp": "2025-03-24T08:19:31.825000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1353644388605231135", "filename": "6.-Blood_Moon-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 31918604, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1353643387810615398/1353644388605231135/6.-Blood_Moon-.wav?ex=69ccd513&is=69cb8393&hm=6389bff68a33eaadf1f5d8d731ac7516d81083404668855b085beab273fe884e&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1353643387810615398", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：薩爾瓦多EP·蒼白的聖徒", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1353644431701708800", "channel_id": "1353643387810615398", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**07.神恩-Saint Grace-**\n仁慈的父啊，我將燃燒我的骨血，焚盡我的靈魂，以作點燃「白焰」的柴薪。\n請將所有苦難加於我身，讓那些迷途的孩子，可以繼續踏上前路。\nMerciful father, I will burn my bones and blood, burn my soul, and use it as firewood to ignite the \"white flame\".\nPlease impose all the suffering on me, so that those lost children can continue on the road.", "timestamp": "2025-03-24T08:19:42.015000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1353644431311507489", "filename": "7.-Saint_Grace-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 24613862, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1353643387810615398/1353644431311507489/7.-Saint_Grace-.wav?ex=69ccd51d&is=69cb839d&hm=cf17da5f78b00537afdc74f3c993dbe5ee197eb72514970a69e20bfd1d916ebd&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1353643387810615398", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：薩爾瓦多EP·蒼白的聖徒", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1353644583040450570", "channel_id": "1353643387810615398", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**08.血肉燈火-Flesh and Flame-**\n審判不會停止，審判必須執行。\n怪物從鏡子中誕生，以自己的血肉為燈芯，將淨化之火傳遍世界。\nJudgment will not stop, and it must be carried out.\nThe monster was born from the mirror, using its own flesh and blood as a wick to spread the fire of purification throughout the world.", "timestamp": "2025-03-24T08:20:18.097000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1353644582629281802", "filename": "8.-Flesh_and_Flame-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 30688496, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1353643387810615398/1353644582629281802/8.-Flesh_and_Flame-.wav?ex=69ccd541&is=69cb83c1&hm=c86725e44f79cefabc0faeb9d6440509e0190b5ebca0ea54368dbc4ff8065071&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1353643387810615398", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：薩爾瓦多EP·蒼白的聖徒", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1353644645955010562", "channel_id": "1353643387810615398", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**09.濟世的白焰-Salvation world's fire-**\n光芒驅散了黑暗，平等地照耀著每位孩子。\n它蒼白，虛弱，卻無比溫暖，充滿力量。\n願這微弱之光，能消去你的苦難，撫平你的內心，我的孩子。\nThe light dispels the darkness and shines equally on every child.\nIt is pale and weak, but extremely warm and full of power.\nMay this faint light eliminate your suffering and soothe your heart, my child.", "timestamp": "2025-03-24T08:20:33.097000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1353644645812408381", "filename": "9.-Salvation_worlds_fire-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 41629334, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1353643387810615398/1353644645812408381/9.-Salvation_worlds_fire-.wav?ex=69ccd551&is=69cb83d1&hm=c89c5aa1a8b1adfb615e888dc5a333f74a5921495092262ac3622ceeba814289&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1353643387810615398", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：薩爾瓦多EP·蒼白的聖徒", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
